info:
  title: BrAPI
  version: ''
openapi: 3.0.0
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    SearchRequestParametersLocations: 
      type: object
      properties:
        locationDbIds:
          description: The location ids to search for
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          example: ['b28911cf', '5071d1e4']
        locationNames:
          description: A human readable names to search for
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          example: ['Location Alpha', 'The Large Hadron Collider']
